先增值，後現金流」作方法，年輕人應投資較多增值類資產，而較年長的，則應投資較多保守類項目，因為年輕人的財富系統未成形，同時負擔較少，可承受的風險度較高，所以會著重增值為先。<br />\n<br />\n你可以考慮月供或分注投資：<br />\n<br />\n盈富（2800）、銀娛（0027）、恆基（0012）、港鐵（0066）、平安（2318）、粵海（0270）、領展（0823）、希慎（0014）、太古地產（1972）等，你可以了解下這些股票，然後從中選股。"},{"pid":"8b45daed6371e5cce29b2d68ff45ea1bd05b2193","tid":2416050,"uid":195023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"All in 美國上市中概股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3664fbcc36787267aee69847ac3feaa24c793e","tid":2416050,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30433b8db79424aa879eba252487a909a8159791","tid":2416050,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"用咗老母身分證開咗個帳號 本金100,000 我買咩老母基本上都睇到 有咩股票推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:06:45.000Z","msg":"長揸TSM，然後努力讀書<br />\n畢業再打開個account會發光"},{"pid":"3f859f57dca0c88b9cb19b0029df103003294d7d","tid":2416050,"uid":248373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T01:05:32.000Z","msg":"又一個少年股神，股災不遠矣！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099b5dab438487257e172ece0ca01aa046e568c1","tid":2416050,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"入門買個GME"},{"pid":"6d076477cc3bf98307964906af49670f3fd3453c","tid":2416050,"uid":198130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099b5dab438487257e172ece0ca01aa046e568c1","tid":2416050,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite